过，有的当时也不太熟的某个小学同学</q></div><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">被盜夢了</span>"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/12/45/124586.jpg","floor":"#28","id":"1221609","time":"2017-3-19 19:15","userId":"124586","userName":"用户","userSign":"(周黑鸭)","message":"你可以选择快进然后开始新剧情<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/01.gif\" smileid=\"40\" alt=\"(bgm24)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/48/274827.jpg","floor":"#29","id":"1221736","time":"2017-3-19 22:07","userId":"kanzoso","userName":"橘花 梨樹","userSign":"","message":"去年的一个梦，醒过来我记下来的：<br>午觉做梦梦见我在中世纪的一个海边的磨坊 半夜<br>我被卷入了一个生存游戏 做错决定就死了 <br><br>第一周目 是个正常结局 最后搭上了逃离的火车<br><br>第二周目 被磨坊主的女儿勾引 没想到是伪娘 亲密时被别人撞个正见 于是我变成女的了 被所有人唾弃 我的单灭结局 <br><br>第三周目 我很小心 没有和任何人过多接触 我的基友和女主走了 抛弃了我 生存游戏的主宰炸了磨坊 把海水放了出去 让大部分人走了 大转换结局<br><br>第四周目 我第四次遇到了第一个会遇见的女角色 应该说是个配角 我发现我已经喜欢上这个角色了 却无法攻略<br><br>我根本不在乎女主 只想让她和我一起走 她告诉我她的使命就是一个传话的配角 要把我送到女主身边<br><br>这个生存游戏的逃离 终究不过是在梦里 就算是和女主 和基友 和大家一起的完美结局也是一场梦 <br><br>然后我就醒了 至于那个女配角 如果她也来到了这个现实世界就好了 无论在何处 只要自由自在便是幸福 这就是我所望的完美结局","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#29-1","id":"1221928","time":"2017-3-20 15:08","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"可以去做游戏了，这个剧本绝对神作啊<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/70.gif\" smileid=\"109\" alt=\"(bgm93)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/48/274827.jpg","floor":"#29-2","id":"1221941","time":"2017-3-20 15:45","userId":"kanzoso","userName":"橘花 梨樹","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 可以去做游戏了，这个剧本绝对神作啊</q></div>还有一个有意思的梦，我记下来的就2个神梦，有空发出来"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#29-3","id":"1221943","time":"2017-3-20 15:45","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">橘 理樹</span> 说: 还有一个有意思的梦，我记下来的就2个神梦，有空发出来</q></div>期待"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/48/274827.jpg","floor":"#30","id":"1221740","time":"2017-3-19 22:10","userId":"kanzoso","userName":"橘花 梨樹","userSign":"","message":"楼主说的重复的梦，在初中时候的确做过。<br>虽然场景变化，但是的确是要去一个找某个特定的女生，不是现实里认识的，是梦里架空的。<br>只可惜到最后也没找到，后来也没有做过类似的梦了。<br><br>大学毕业后，做10个梦有9个是学生年代的生活，真怀念读书的时光。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#30-1","id":"1221927","time":"2017-3-20 15:07","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q>大学毕业后，做10个梦有9个是学生年代的生活，真怀念读书的时光。</q></div>我跟你讲我昨晚梦到高中考试迟到一个小时，醒过来发现是梦真是长舒一口气"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/48/274827.jpg","floor":"#30-2","id":"1221942","time":"2017-3-20 15:45","userId":"kanzoso","userName":"橘花 梨樹","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 我跟你讲我昨晚梦到高中考试迟到一个小时，醒过来发现是梦真是长舒一口气</q></div>我还梦到又要高考了。。。"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#30-3","id":"1221944","time":"2017-3-20 15:47","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">橘 理樹</span> 说: 我还梦到又要高考了。。。</q></div>我好像也是梦到高考语文来着，醒过来太久记不清楚了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/16.gif\" smileid=\"55\" alt=\"(bgm39)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/02/68/26866.jpg","floor":"#31","id":"1221774","time":"2017-3-19 23:37","userId":"hc","userName":"月火","userSign":"(おのれ！これで勝ったと思うなよぉ!!! ...)","message":"有<br>第一晚梦到有个白人短髮小孩站在厨房中，用凶恶的眼神望向我，一动也不动<br>第二晚梦到有个白人老人站在相同位置，用凶恶的眼神望向我，一动也不动<br>没有之后了，现实中也没有发生任何怪事","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#31-1","id":"1221926","time":"2017-3-20 15:06","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"……好吓人"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/68/286878.jpg","floor":"#32","id":"1221793","time":"2017-3-20 01:52","userId":"yejingchen","userName":"菜叶","userSign":"(你的爱还不够啊！)","message":"我是有一个平淡无奇的梦从小到大做了好几遍…不过每次梦里我的行动都会推进一点点<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br><br>梦里的内容大概是这样的：某天的黄昏我站在家旁边河流的一侧，斜向上地望着对面的楼房和天空，还有对岸的一个建筑工地的吊塔的机械臂，天空的颜色是橙色和黑色的渐变，而楼房和机械臂就是累死水墨画的黑色了。<br><br>这个颜色和背景可能来自于当时在玩的流行之神2雪乃的公寓那张背景图吧<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">毕竟这游戏给小学的我留下了很深的印象。<br>机械臂则可能是小时候很喜欢模仿挖掘机的机械臂抓来抓取吧(Bgm38)妈妈还夸我学得像来着，不过现实中河对岸并没有那二十几层高的楼房（也许是深圳的楼房楼下的印象？）<br><br>第一次做这个梦的时候我只是站在这边的岸上望着对岸，特别是对岸的机械臂，不过除此之外什么都没做。<br><br>过了几年(?)第二次做这个梦的时候我有就打算走到最面那个机械臂的位子了，不过我从河这边找了找找到我家路口的那座桥之后就醒了（或者说不记得了）。<br><br>第三次梦到时我正在小巷中穿行，应该是过到了河对岸，抬头看到的楼房缝间的天空、以及整个画面的色调都是之前的橙黄色，小巷既有点像家周围的巷子一样有点像某个动漫的画风…走着走着突然感觉有人追我，拼命跑着跑着就没有下文了 。<br><br>在第四次、也是目前为止最新的一次里，我意识到我在梦里时已经站在那吊塔高高的机械臂上了，周围还是那橙黄色，我从机械臂上望着底下的河水（还是第三人称视角？），又是无事发生。<br><br>不知道今晚会不会做第五次梦呀(Bgm38)","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/02/204.jpg","floor":"#32-1","id":"1221795","time":"2017-3-20 02:19","userId":"mono","userName":"rnono","userSign":"","message":"好像恐怖故事!"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/68/286878.jpg","floor":"#32-2","id":"1221819","time":"2017-3-20 08:35","userId":"yejingchen","userName":"菜叶","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">mono</span> 说: 好像恐怖故事!</q></div>然而昨晚什么梦都没做（早上还迟到了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/71/227195.jpg","floor":"#32-3","id":"1221906","time":"2017-3-20 13:31","userId":"227195","userName":"thofoofintwsi","userSign":"","message":"为什么小学就玩流行之神啊。。。不应该是魂斗罗什么的吗"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#32-4","id":"1221925","time":"2017-3-20 15:06","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">mono</span> 说: 好像恐怖故事!</q></div>我觉得月火那个更像<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/16.gif\" smileid=\"55\" alt=\"(bgm39)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/68/286878.jpg","floor":"#32-5","id":"1222009","time":"2017-3-20 21:01","userId":"yejingchen","userName":"菜叶","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">thofoofintwsi</span> 说: 为什么小学就玩流行之神啊。。。不应该是魂斗罗什么的吗</q></div>刚刚拿到了 PSP 想找游戏玩嘛，结果撞上了一个大坑，现在也成了有生之年系列了 <img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/68/286878.jpg","floor":"#32-6","id":"1222010","time":"2017-3-20 21:02","userId":"yejingchen","userName":"菜叶","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">thofoofintwsi</span> 说: 为什么小学就玩流行之神啊。。。不应该是魂斗罗什么的吗</q></div>我挺想知道后续的来着（"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/28/31/283154.jpg","floor":"#33","id":"1221796","time":"2017-3-20 02:48","userId":"283154","userName":"wolfsring","userSign":"","message":"成为人生赢家这种梦 高中以后就不再重复了","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#33-1","id":"1221924","time":"2017-3-20 15:05","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"看清了人生的真相是吗<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/16.gif\" smileid=\"55\" alt=\"(bgm39)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/59/135935.jpg","floor":"#34","id":"1221801","time":"2017-3-20 05:31","userId":"simoun","userName":"夢我夢中","userSign":"(亲子关系一旦确定,就开始了人生悲剧的第一章。 ... .. ...)","message":"有，做梦到一半发现这梦以前做过·····然后醒悟自己在做梦···然后并没有什么鸟用···走完既定流程醒了","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#34-1","id":"1221930","time":"2017-3-20 15:09","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"梦到一半发现自己是在做梦能自主醒过来吗<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/16.gif\" smileid=\"55\" alt=\"(bgm39)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/59/135935.jpg","floor":"#34-2","id":"1222072","time":"2017-3-21 02:44","userId":"simoun","userName":"夢我夢中","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 梦到一半发现自己是在做梦能自主醒过来吗</q></div>能吧。美梦只想一直继续下去，噩梦才想快点醒过来，这种时候努力想象最恐惧的发展，就可以直接迎来最终BE，在SAN值降到0之前惊醒过来。 不过照自己身上的经历来看最可怕的是，当自己以为逃离了噩梦苏醒过来，却发现身处一片黑暗之中，躺在床上。想要爬起来，手脚却不受一点控制，在黑暗和寂静中再次被恐惧和绝望支配，然后···就真的惊醒了"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/46/134645.jpg","floor":"#35","id":"1221809","time":"2017-3-20 07:31","userId":"pk8810","userName":"佩卡","userSign":"(原来作者你们都是真的蕾丝啊(怪不得写那么好 ...)","message":"高中前倒是经常会做重复的梦，现在完全不会。。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/22/95/229592.jpg","floor":"#36","id":"1221838","time":"2017-3-20 09:20","userId":"sprinter","userName":"疾走狂徒","userSign":"(当笨蛋超爽der~)","message":"做梦这件事本身就不常有···<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/11.gif\" smileid=\"50\" alt=\"(bgm34)\">","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/16/71697.jpg","floor":"#37","id":"1221840","time":"2017-3-20 09:23","userId":"mucc","userName":"矮木油希希","userSign":"(都是异端！)","message":"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">我已经连续梦到好几天刷武器改造材料刷不到了……","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/42/14268.jpg","floor":"#37-1","id":"1221853","time":"2017-3-20 09:52","userId":"calfn","userName":"触触✅个人认证","userSign":"","message":"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">还有救吗我的爱木有吸吸"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/16/71697.jpg","floor":"#37-2","id":"1221882","time":"2017-3-20 12:17","userId":"mucc","userName":"矮木油希希","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">柳胜薰CALFN-触触小可爱VIP</span> 说: 还有救吗我的爱木有吸吸</q></div><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">DLC一入怕是没有了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/42/14268.jpg","floor":"#37-3","id":"1221888","time":"2017-3-20 12:39","userId":"calfn","userName":"触触✅个人认证","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">矮木油希希</span> 说: DLC一入怕是没有了</q></div>爱木有吸吸你还需要嫁人吗"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/16/71697.jpg","floor":"#37-4","id":"1221889","time":"2017-3-20 12:40","userId":"mucc","userName":"矮木油希希","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">柳胜薰CALFN-触触小可爱VIP</span> 说: 爱木有吸吸你还需要嫁人吗</q></div>不，我发现我根本不需要……"},{"avatar"